('97974','33807','5','Newly renovated golf villa at the golf course Santa Ponsa for sale'),
('97975','33808','5','In a very popular golf residence in Santa Ponsa is this beautifull, in 2015 renovated Golf Villa. She has approximately 180m² of living space, spread over the main living level with living-dining room, modern fitted kitchen, utility room, guest toilet, 2 bedrooms with a bathroom en suite, winter garden and separate guest rooms with bathroom and terrace on the 1st floor. In the middle of a landscaped garden is the priv. Pool. Furthermore, it still has a Finnish- and a steam sauna. The interior and exterior floor was tiled with bright tiles, which gives this villa an elegant look. The garage has space for 1 car and a golf cart. The technical equipment includes an electric. underfloor heating, air conditioning w / c, fireplace casette, climalit double glazed windows and a chic, white fitted kitchen'),
